---
title: Honey Harissa Glazed Salmon with Garlic Bulgur, Charred Courgette and Yoghurt
description: This Honey Harissa Glazed Salmon is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R11_W20_UK_HVP19185-4_Main__4low-be4319cf.jpg
